308725252.Title: Galanz 12.0 cu. ft. Top Freezer Retro Refrigerator with Dual Door True Freezer, Frost Free in Red
308725252.Description: Galanz 12.0 cu. ft. Retro style frost free top freezer refrigerator can store and keep cool snacks, beverages and more. Best of all, this refrigerator-freezer has the look and feel of the fabulous old days, but has the appeal of a modern appliance. Featuring an adjustable thermostat, separate freezer compartment, bright interior lighting and spacious, clear fruit and vegetable crisper, the unit also has removable shelves and door shelves. It is a fun and stylish addition to any kitchen, rec room or home office!. Color: Red.

305756388.Title: Summit Appliance 10.3 cu. ft. Frost Free Top Freezer Refrigerator In Black
305756388.Description: The FF1119BIM makes the ideal addition to any household kitchen looking for full storage capacity in a hard-to-find fit. Made in North America, this two-door refrigerator-freezer brings true convenience into the home. Frost-free operation ensures low maintenance, while the interior is fully equipped with adjustable shelves, a large crisper, interior light, and door storage in both compartments. This model includes a factory installed icemaker. At just 24 in. wide and under 60 in. high, the FF1119BIM is perfectly sized for any location, including those complying with ADA guidelines for accessibility. This unit comes in a jet black finish with user-reversible doors.

311651935.Title: Danby 10.1 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in Stainless Steel, Counter Depth, Stainless Look
311651935.Description: This apartment-sized refrigerator by Danby is second to none when it comes to performance and looks. It provides a generous 10.1 cu. ft. of refrigeration space as well as a classy design that can fit in with any existing decor. The DFF101 series features a convenient frost free-operation system, so you can enjoy maintenance free use while preventing ice buildup. These fridges come with a pair of removable and adjustable glass shelves as well as a removable wire shelf in the freezer compartment. Additionally, 2-vegetable crispers are offered for optimal storage. Color: Stainless Look.
